description: This file contains Java Data Transfer Object (DTO) classes for user operations within a note management backend project, including classes for registration, login, authentication response, and user response.

classes.name: UserDtos
classes.description: Container class for user-related DTOs used in API requests and responses.

classes.name: RegisterRequest
classes.description: DTO for user registration requests, including username, email, and password.

classes.name: LoginRequest
classes.description: DTO for user login requests, containing username and password.

classes.name: AuthResponse
classes.description: DTO for authentication response, including user ID, username, email, and token.

classes.name: UserResponse
classes.description: DTO for representing user data in responses, including user ID, username, and email.
